gate.swing

Class JTreeTable.MouseHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.event.MouseAdapter
      • gate.swing.JTreeTable.MouseHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MouseListener, MouseMotionListener, MouseWheelListener, EventListener
    Enclosing class:
    JTreeTable

     class JTreeTable.MouseHandler
extends MouseAdapter
    Class used to convert the mouse events from the JTreeTable component space into the JTree space. It is used to forward the mouse events to the tree if they occured in the space used by the tree.
